---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout>
  <section class="container mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">About</h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-lg muted-theme">I'm Guru Nikhil Mangaraju, a Full Stack Developer and Computer Science student focused on building reliable, user-friendly web applications and AI-enabled developer tools. I enjoy turning ideas into polished products, with a special interest in APIs, scalable architectures, and applying machine learning to practical problems.</p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">What I do</h3>
  <p class="text-sm muted-theme mt-2">I build full-stack applications using modern JavaScript frameworks, design clean RESTful APIs and GraphQL endpoints, and integrate AI features such as content generation, summarization, and intelligent search into products. I like simple, testable code and shipping small iterations quickly.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Tech & tools</h3>
  <p class="text-sm muted-theme mt-2">Next.js · React · Node.js · TypeScript · Tailwind · GraphQL · RESTful APIs · Firebase · PostgreSQL · Docker · Vercel</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Selected experience</h3>
  <p class="text-sm muted-theme mt-2">Full Stack Developer Intern, Aegion Dynamic Solutions (Jan 2025 - Jun 2025): contributed to core web features, API design, and deployment automation. Built the AI-driven Hackin and LearnSphere projects (links on the Projects page).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Get in touch</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">I’m open to collaborations, internships, and freelance work. <a href="/contact" class="text-[var(--blue)]">Contact me</a> or check my <a href="https://github.com/MGuruNikhil" class="text-[var(--blue)]">GitHub</a> for recent work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
